[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     96[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def ingest_slide(bucket: str, key: str) -> str:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     97[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     98[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Register a new whole slide image and queue it for analysis.
